name: cardstyle15, card-style for the 1.5 checkpoint.
description:
Requested 1.5 checkpoint version of the card-style embedding I created for 2.1 768. Using the same dataset resized to 512x512.

Trained using the v1-5-pruned.ckpt checkpoint.

modelVersions.name: cardstyle15
modelVersions.description: All images are txt2img using the v1-5-pruned-emaonly.ckpt checkpoint and the DPM++ 2M Karras sampler.
